PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 31 - which (a) DECLARES the severe flooding in southern NEW BRUNSWICK which occured in March 1998, to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.

precis:
Enactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 31 -
which (a) DECLARES the severe flooding in southern NEW BRUNSWICK which
occured in March 1998, to be of concern to the federal government, and
(b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
